display_long_description:
# The walls close in, and so will they...
In this heart-pounding, claustrophobia-inducing VR horror experience you are trapped deep underground. Armed with only your wits, you’ll explore suffocating tunnels and encounter horrors lurking in the shadows. Will you escape with your sanity intact, or will the tunnels claim you and your friends forever?

# Immersive Single-Player Adventure

**Claustrophobic Terror** – Fight to keep your sanity as the mine tunnels collapse and the creatures within them come for you.

**Horror Unique to VR** - Immerse yourself in boundary-pushing VR gameplay as you embark on a story-driven plunge into suffocating darkness, relying solely on a lone voice over the radio to survive.

**A Caving Adventure** – Plunge into eerie underground lakes, zipline over bottomless chasms, and scale sheer cliffs—all while evading the nightmarish creatures lurking in the depths.



# Chaotic and Fun Free-To-Play Multiplayer

**Free-to-Play Multiplayer** – Team up with friends and strangers in the online co-op mode where your survival depends on teamwork… or betrayal.

**Customize Your Survivor** – Customize your character with unique gear and show off your style as you and your friends confront the mine’s horrors together.

**Frequent Content Updates** - Even more multiplayer fun with new levels, exciting cosmetics, and regular content updates, our free-to-play multiplayer will get even better as time goes on!
